OL,3,CHolidaymaker faces #160,000 hospital
OL,4,Cbill after being stabbed in head
OL,6,FTharel Thompson's mother, Yvonne, has
OL,7,Fbeen speaking to ITV Meridian's Wesley
OL,8,FSmith.
OL,10,FThe mother of a man who sustained life-
OL,11,Fchanging injuries when he was stabbed
OL,12,Fin the head in an attack in Reading,
OL,13,Fhas been telling ITV News Meridian of
OL,14,Fthe devastating impact it's had on
OL,15,Ftheir lives.
OL,17,FTharel Thompson, who's 29, had come on
OL,18,Fholiday to the UK from his home in
OL,19,FBarbados and had only been here three
OL,20,Fdays when the attack happened on
OL,21,FSunday 11th February 2024.
