OL,4,Cbill after being stabbed in head
OL,6,FHis life nearly came to an end when he
OL,7,Fwas viciously stabbed in the head in
OL,8,Fan unprovoked attack by Krisma Anthony
OL,9,Fat the Walkabout Bar in Reading Town
OL,10,FCentre.
OL,12,FTharel remembers little of that day,
OL,13,Fbut he is all too aware of the
OL,14,Fdevastating impact on his life and
OL,15,Fthat of his mother, Yvonne.
OL,17,FAs soon as she heard the news of his
OL,18,Flife-threatening injuries, she flew
OL,19,Fstraight over from home in Barbados to
OL,20,Flook after her only child.
