OL,6,FSince then, she's had to give up her
OL,7,Fhome and job and is living with family
OL,8,Ffriends, but says it's what any mother
OL,9,Fwould do.
OL,11,F"It's a call that no parent would want
OL,12,Fto hear, mother, father, no parent at
OL,13,Fall. It was very heart-wrenching,"
OL,14,Fsaid Yvonne Thompson.
OL,16,F"He has to continue his
OL,17,Frehabilitation, he needs to get
OL,18,Fphysical, occupational and
OL,19,Fpsychological therapy."
