OL,6,F"There is no movement in his hand at
OL,7,Fall because of the massive stroke he
OL,8,Fhad."
OL,10,F"Right now he has to wear a helmet all
OL,11,Fthe time to protect anything from
OL,12,Ftouching his head and that's something
OL,13,Fhe's very scared about, anything
OL,14,Ftouching his head at all."
OL,16,FYvonne Thompson is just taking things
OL,17,Fone day at a time.
OL,19,F"I've been in my job for 19 years and
OL,20,FI don't know what is going to happen
OL,21,Fthere."
