OL,6,FShe fears that Tharel will not be able
OL,7,Fto return to his stage lighting job
OL,8,Feither.
OL,10,FShe says the 27 year sentence given to
OL,11,Fhis attacker helps a bit but is still
OL,12,Fleft with questions.
OL,14,F"The whole incident was just
OL,15,Funnecessary, I just don't know why. He
OL,16,Fjust came for a vacation."
OL,18,F"Not that it should happen to anyone
OL,19,Felse but why pick him of all the
OL,20,Fthousands of people in this city."
