OL,6,FTharel now faces further brain surgery
OL,7,Fat the John Radcliffe Hospital in
OL,8,FOxford. The cost of his care is
OL,9,Fexpected to cost more than #160,000 as
OL,10,Fhe's not eligible for free NHS
OL,11,Ftreatment.
OL,13,FTharel didn't have holiday insurance,
OL,14,Fso now faces a bill for essential
OL,15,Fsurgery in Oxford which isn't
OL,16,Favailable at home.
OL,18,FThe family has set up a GoFundMe page
OL,19,Fin his name in the hope of charity
OL,20,Fdonations.
