OL,6,F"He deserves a second chance at life,"
OL,7,Fsaid Yvonne, "It's very hard but every
OL,8,Fday I remind myself it's not going to
OL,9,Fbe like this all the time."
OL,11,F"The day is going to come, he is going
OL,12,Fto get better and that is what keeps
OL,13,Fme going."
OL,15,FThe road ahead is a long one, but
OL,16,FYvonne and Tharel say they couldn't
OL,17,Fhave got this far without the generous
OL,18,Fsupport of friends, strangers and the
OL,19,Fmedical teams at the Royal Berkshire
OL,20,Fand John Radcliffe Hospitals.
